            </nav>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Overview Section -->
    <section id="overview" class="mb-5">
        <h2>Overview</h2>
        <p>
            The Graded Quiz feature provides a formal assessment mode where your performance is tracked and scored. 
            Unlike the practice Quiz, the Graded Quiz records your answers, calculates your percentage, and provides 
            detailed results at the end with explanations for all questions.
        </p>
        <div class="alert alert-warning" role="alert">
            <h5 class="alert-heading">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" fill="currentColor" class="bi bi-exclamation-triangle me-2" viewBox="0 0 16 16">
                    <path d="M7.938 2.016A.13.13 0 0 1 8.002 2a.13.13 0 0 1 .063.016.146.146 0 0 1 .054.057l6.857 11.667c.036.06.035.124.002.183a.163.163 0 0 1-.054.06.116.116 0 0 1-.066.017H1.146a.115.115 0 0 1-.066-.017.163.163 0 0 1-.054-.06.176.176 0 0 1 .002-.183L7.884 2.073a.147.147 0 0 1 .054-.057zm1.044-.45a1.13 1.13 0 0 0-1.96 0L.165 13.233c-.457.778.091 1.767.98 1.767h13.713c.889 0 1.438-.99.98-1.767L8.982 1.566z"/>
                    <path d="M7.002 12a1 1 0 1 1 2 0 1 1 0 0 1-2 0zM7.1 5.995a.905.905 0 1 1 1.8 0l-.35 3.507a.552.552 0 0 1-1.1 0L7.1 5.995z"/>
                </svg>
                Important
            </h5>
            <p class="mb-0">
                Once you start a Graded Quiz, you must complete all questions in one session. You won't see feedback 
                until you finish the entire quiz and view your results.
            </p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Getting Started Section -->
    <section id="getting-started" class="mb-5">
        <div class="card">
            <div class="card-header bg-danger text-white">
                <h3 class="mb-0">Getting Started</h3>
            </div>
            <div class="card-body">
                <ol class="list-group list-group-numbered">
                    <li class="list-group-item">
                        <strong>Navigate to Graded Quiz:</strong> From the home page, click the "Graded Quiz" button.
                        <p class="mb-0 text-muted">You'll see the setup page where you can choose the number of questions.</p>
                    </li>
                    <li class="list-group-item">
                        <strong>Select Question Count:</strong> Choose how many questions you want (1-50).
                        <p class="mb-0 text-muted">More questions provide a more comprehensive assessment.</p>
                    </li>
                    <li class="list-group-item">
                        <strong>Start the Quiz:</strong> Click "Start Quiz" to begin.
                        <p class="mb-0 text-muted">Your quiz session starts immediately and the timer begins.</p>
                    </li>
                    <li class="list-group-item">
                        <strong>Answer Each Question:</strong> Select one answer per question and click "Submit Answer".
                        <p class="mb-0 text-muted">You'll advance to the next question automatically.</p>
                    </li>
                    <li class="list-group-item">
                        <strong>Complete the Quiz:</strong> Continue until you've answered all questions.
                        <p class="mb-0 text-muted">You'll be redirected to the results page automatically.</p>
                    </li>
                </ol>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Taking the Quiz Section -->
    <section id="taking-quiz" class="mb-5">
        <h2>Taking the Quiz</h2>
        <p>
            During the Graded Quiz, focus on answering each question carefully. Unlike practice mode, you won't receive 
            immediate feedback—your answers are recorded and reviewed at the end.
        </p>
        <h4>What You'll See:</h4>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Progress Bar:</strong> Shows how many questions you've completed (e.g., "Question 5 of 20").</li>
            <li><strong>Score Tracker:</strong> Displays your current correct and incorrect counts.</li>
            <li><strong>Question Text:</strong> The question and four possible answers.</li>
            <li><strong>Answer Selection:</strong> Radio buttons or clickable options to select your answer.</li>
            <li><strong>Submit Button:</strong> Submits your answer and advances to the next question.</li>
        </ul>
        <div class="alert alert-info" role="alert">
            <h5 class="alert-heading">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" fill="currentColor" class="bi bi-info-circle me-2" viewBox="0 0 16 16">
                    <path d="M8 15A7 7 0 1 1 8 1a7 7 0 0 1 0 14zm0 1A8 8 0 1 0 8 0a8 8 0 0 0 0 16z"/>
                    <path d="m8.93 6.588-2.29.287-.082.38.45.083c.294.07.352.176.288.469l-.738 3.468c-.194.897.105 1.319.808 1.319.545 0 1.178-.252 1.465-.598l.088-.416c-.2.176-.492.246-.686.246-.275 0-.375-.193-.304-.533L8.93 6.588zM9 4.5a1 1 0 1 1-2 0 1 1 0 0 1 2 0z"/>
                </svg>
                Note
            </h5>
            <p class="mb-0">
                You cannot go back to previous questions or change your answers once submitted. Make sure you're 
                confident in your choice before clicking "Submit Answer".
            </p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Results Section -->
    <section id="results" class="mb-5">
        <h2>Understanding Your Results</h2>
        <p>
            After completing all questions, you'll see a comprehensive results page showing your performance and 
            detailed explanations for every question.
        </p>
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-6 mb-3">
                <div class="card border-primary">
                    <div class="card-header bg-primary text-white">
                        <h5 class="mb-0">Score Summary</h5>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <p>At the top of the results page, you'll see:</p>
                        <ul>
                            <li><strong>Total Score:</strong> Percentage (e.g., "75%")</li>
                            <li><strong>Correct Answers:</strong> Number you got right</li>
                            <li><strong>Incorrect Answers:</strong> Number you got wrong</li>
                            <li><strong>Performance Rating:</strong> Excellent, Good, Fair, or Needs Improvement</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6 mb-3">
                <div class="card border-success">
                    <div class="card-header bg-success text-white">
                        <h5 class="mb-0">Question Review</h5>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <p>Below the summary, you'll see all questions with:</p>
                        <ul>
                            <li><strong>Your Answer:</strong> What you selected</li>
                            <li><strong>Correct Answer:</strong> The right choice</li>
                            <li><strong>Explanation:</strong> Why the answer is correct</li>
                            <li><strong>Correctness Indicator:</strong> Green checkmark or red X</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <h4>Performance Ratings:</h4>
        <ul>
            <li><span class="badge bg-success">Excellent</span> - 90% or higher</li>
            <li><span class="badge bg-info">Good</span> - 70-89%</li>
            <li><span class="badge bg-warning text-dark">Fair</span> - 50-69%</li>
            <li><span class="badge bg-danger">Needs Improvement</span> - Below 50%</li>
        </ul>
    </section>

    <!-- Tips & Best Practices Section -->
    <section id="tips" class="mb-5">
        <h2>Tips & Best Practices</h2>
        <div class="card mb-3">
            <div class="card-body">
                <h5 class="card-title">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" fill="currentColor" class="bi bi-star text-warning me-2" viewBox="0 0 16 16">
                        <path d="M2.866 14.85c-.078.444.36.791.746.593l4.39-2.256 4.389 2.256c.386.198.824-.149.746-.592l-.83-4.73 3.522-3.356c.33-.314.16-.888-.282-.95l-4.898-.696L8.465.792a.513.513 0 0 0-.927 0L5.354 5.12l-4.898.696c-.441.062-.612.636-.283.95l3.523 3.356-.83 4.73zm4.905-2.767-3.686 1.894.694-3.957a.565.565 0 0 0-.163-.505L1.71 6.745l4.052-.576a.525.525 0 0 0 .393-.288L8 2.223l1.847 3.658a.525.525 0 0 0 .393.288l4.052.575-2.906 2.77a.565.565 0 0 0-.163.506l.694 3.957-3.686-1.894a.503.503 0 0 0-.461 0z"/>
                    </svg>
                    Practice First
                </h5>
                <p class="card-text">
                    Use the regular Quiz feature to practice before taking a Graded Quiz. This helps you become familiar 
                    with the question format and difficulty level.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card mb-3">
            <div class="card-body">
                <h5 class="card-title">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" fill="currentColor" class="bi bi-star text-warning me-2" viewBox="0 0 16 16">
                        <path d="M2.866 14.85c-.078.444.36.791.746.593l4.39-2.256 4.389 2.256c.386.198.824-.149.746-.592l-.83-4.73 3.522-3.356c.33-.314.16-.888-.282-.95l-4.898-.696L8.465.792a.513.513 0 0 0-.927 0L5.354 5.12l-4.898.696c-.441.062-.612.636-.283.95l3.523 3.356-.83 4.73zm4.905-2.767-3.686 1.894.694-3.957a.565.565 0 0 0-.163-.505L1.71 6.745l4.052-.576a.525.525 0 0 0 .393-.288L8 2.223l1.847 3.658a.525.525 0 0 0 .393.288l4.052.575-2.906 2.77a.565.565 0 0 0-.163.506l.694 3.957-3.686-1.894a.503.503 0 0 0-.461 0z"/>
                    </svg>
                    Read Carefully
                </h5>
                <p class="card-text">
                    Since you can't go back, read each question and all answer choices thoroughly before making your selection.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card mb-3">
            <div class="card-body">
                <h5 class="card-title">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" fill="currentColor" class="bi bi-star text-warning me-2" viewBox="0 0 16 16">
                        <path d="M2.866 14.85c-.078.444.36.791.746.593l4.39-2.256 4.389 2.256c.386.198.824-.149.746-.592l-.83-4.73 3.522-3.356c.33-.314.16-.888-.282-.95l-4.898-.696L8.465.792a.513.513 0 0 0-.927 0L5.354 5.12l-4.898.696c-.441.062-.612.636-.283.95l3.523 3.356-.83 4.73zm4.905-2.767-3.686 1.894.694-3.957a.565.565 0 0 0-.163-.505L1.71 6.745l4.052-.576a.525.525 0 0 0 .393-.288L8 2.223l1.847 3.658a.525.525 0 0 0 .393.288l4.052.575-2.906 2.77a.565.565 0 0 0-.163.506l.694 3.957-3.686-1.894a.503.503 0 0 0-.461 0z"/>
                    </svg>
                    Review Results Thoroughly
                </h5>
                <p class="card-text">
                    After completing the quiz, read all explanations—even for questions you got right. This reinforces 
                    your understanding and helps you remember key concepts.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card mb-3">
            <div class="card-body">
                <h5 class="card-title">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" fill="currentColor" class="bi bi-star text-warning me-2" viewBox="0 0 16 16">
                        <path d="M2.866 14.85c-.078.444.36.791.746.593l4.39-2.256 4.389 2.256c.386.198.824-.149.746-.592l-.83-4.73 3.522-3.356c.33-.314.16-.888-.282-.95l-4.898-.696L8.465.792a.513.513 0 0 0-.927 0L5.354 5.12l-4.898.696c-.441.062-.612.636-.283.95l3.523 3.356-.83 4.73zm4.905-2.767-3.686 1.894.694-3.957a.565.565 0 0 0-.163-.505L1.71 6.745l4.052-.576a.525.525 0 0 0 .393-.288L8 2.223l1.847 3.658a.525.525 0 0 0 .393.288l4.052.575-2.906 2.77a.565.565 0 0 0-.163.506l.694 3.957-3.686-1.894a.503.503 0 0 0-.461 0z"/>
                    </svg>
                    Retake if Needed
                </h5>
                <p class="card-text">
                    If your score is below your goal, use the "Retake Quiz" button to try again. The questions will be 
                    different, giving you a fresh assessment.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Troubleshooting Section -->
    <section id="troubleshooting" class="mb-5">
        <h2>Troubleshooting</h2>
        <div class="accordion" id="troubleshootingAccordion">
            <div class="accordion-item">
                <h2 class="accordion-header">
                    <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#problem1">
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" fill="currentColor" class="bi bi-exclamation-circle me-2 text-danger" viewBox="0 0 16 16">
                            <path d="M8 15A7 7 0 1 1 8 1a7 7 0 0 1 0 14zm0 1A8 8 0 1 0 8 0a8 8 0 0 0 0 16z"/>
                            <path d="M7.002 11a1 1 0 1 1 2 0 1 1 0 0 1-2 0zM7.1 4.995a.905.905 0 1 1 1.8 0l-.35 3.507a.552.552 0 0 1-1.1 0L7.1 4.995z"/>
                        </svg>
                        Problem: Quiz session was lost or interrupted
                    </button>
                </h2>
                <div id="problem1" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#troubleshootingAccordion">
                    <div class="accordion-body">
                        <p><strong>Solution:</strong> If your browser closed or you navigated away, your session may be lost.</p>
                        <ul>
                            <li>The Graded Quiz uses session storage; closing the browser ends the session</li>
                            <li>Try to complete the quiz in one sitting without closing the browser</li>
                            <li>If interrupted, you'll need to start a new quiz from the setup page</li>
                            <li>Your previous attempt won't be saved if not completed</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="accordion-item">
                <h2 class="accordion-header">
                    <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#problem2">
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" fill="currentColor" class="bi bi-exclamation-circle me-2 text-danger" viewBox="0 0 16 16">
                            <path d="M8 15A7 7 0 1 1 8 1a7 7 0 0 1 0 14zm0 1A8 8 0 1 0 8 0a8 8 0 0 0 0 16z"/>
                            <path d="M7.002 11a1 1 0 1 1 2 0 1 1 0 0 1-2 0zM7.1 4.995a.905.905 0 1 1 1.8 0l-.35 3.507a.552.552 0 0 1-1.1 0L7.1 4.995z"/>
                        </svg>
                        Problem: Results page not showing
                    </button>
                </h2>
                <div id="problem2" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#troubleshootingAccordion">
                    <div class="accordion-body">
                        <p><strong>Solution:</strong> Ensure you completed all questions before expecting results.</p>
                        <ul>
                            <li>You must answer every question in the quiz to see results</li>
                            <li>Check the progress bar to confirm you've reached the last question</li>
                            <li>If you see an error, try retaking the quiz from the setup page</li>
                            <li>Clear your browser cache if the issue persists</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="accordion-item">
                <h2 class="accordion-header">
                    <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#problem3">
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" fill="currentColor" class="bi bi-exclamation-circle me-2 text-danger" viewBox="0 0 16 16">
                            <path d="M8 15A7 7 0 1 1 8 1a7 7 0 0 1 0 14zm0 1A8 8 0 1 0 8 0a8 8 0 0 0 0 16z"/>
                            <path d="M7.002 11a1 1 0 1 1 2 0 1 1 0 0 1-2 0zM7.1 4.995a.905.905 0 1 1 1.8 0l-.35 3.507a.552.552 0 0 1-1.1 0L7.1 4.995z"/>
                        </svg>
                        Problem: Can't select an answer
                    </button>
                </h2>
                <div id="problem3" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#troubleshootingAccordion">
                    <div class="accordion-body">
                        <p><strong>Solution:</strong> Try these steps if answer selection isn't working:</p>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Refresh the page (you may need to restart the quiz)</li>
                            <li>Clear browser cache and cookies</li>
                            <li>Try a different browser (Chrome, Firefox, Edge, Safari)</li>
                            <li>Ensure JavaScript is enabled</li>
                            <li>Check your internet connection</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Related Topics Section -->
    <section id="related" class="mb-5">
        <div class="card bg-light">
            <div class="card-header">
                <h3 class="mb-0">Related Topics</h3>
            </div>
            <div class="card-body">
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-md-6 mb-3">
                        <div class="card h-100">
                            <div class="card-body">
                                <h5 class="card-title">
                                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" fill="currentColor" class="bi bi-question-circle text-primary me-2" viewBox="0 0 16 16">
