                                    Graded Exercises
                                </h5>
                                <p class="card-text">Prefer solving problems over multiple-choice? Try the Graded Exercises feature.</p>
                                <a asp-controller="Help" asp-action="GradedExercises" class="btn btn-sm btn-outline-primary">Learn More →</a>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-6 mb-3">
                        <div class="card h-100">
                            <div class="card-body">
